        <hl1>The best, the brightest and 'The Bell Curve.'</hl1>
      </hedline>
    </body.head>
    <body.content>
      <block class="lead_paragraph">
        <p>To the Editor:</p>
        <p>Any intelligence test on which high scores can be achieved by people capable of believing in anything so preposterous as the efficacy of intelligence tests is obviously fundamentally and irremediably flawed. JEFFERY EWENER  Toronto</p>
